ActFirst Nations Goods and Services Tax Act
SubjectOrder Amending Schedule 1 to the First Nations Goods and Services Tax Act, No. 2014-2 (Neskonlith)
PrecisOrder Amending SCHEDULE 1 TO THE FIRST NATIONS GOODS AND SERVICES TAX ACT, NO. 2014-2 (NESKONLITH) in order to enable Neskonlith, with the agreement of the Government of Canada, to implement the First Nations Goods and Services tax within its lands.
